and I need your love tonight, and I need you more than ever

I released this and deleted it shortly after to make it more enjoyable to play. I'll have a harder map on the way sometime.

Thanks to Saspatoon, Pcpie, Zyper, Sinful, Guadalupe, Whimsy, and probably more people for helping me whenever I asked.

Feedback is appreciated, I'd like to know what you guys like and dislike about the map. :)
